{"id":128355,"type":6,"name":"十七岁不哭","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/46/61/128355_CUaIi.jpg","summary":"　　这是一群十七岁男生女生的故事。班长简宁（李晨 饰）成绩优秀，勤奋自勉；杨宇凌（郝蕾 饰）伶俐能干，敢怒敢言；雷蒙（张超 饰）问题多多，桀骜不驯；晓丹（牛萌萌 饰）文静内向；乐心（王卓 饰）林林（陈嫣嫣 饰）一个活泼一个娇气……这群性格各异的同学在新学校开始了他们的新生活。如同所有的高中生一样，他们经历军训、突击的模拟考、初次的集体生活，有学习上的困扰，对未来既憧憬又迷茫；他们朝气蓬勃，追求新鲜事物，有说不完的话讲不完的故事；他们走在花季雨季，经历陌生的感情，触碰青涩的梦。十七岁的他们一边受伤一边学会坚强，翩翩少年开花要结果，他们日渐成长。 \r\n　　本剧根据当年十七岁的女中学生李芳芳的同名小说改编。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>十七岁不哭</li><li><span>主演: </span>郝蕾 / 牛萌萌 / <a href=\"/person/17196\">李晨</a> / 张超 / 王卓 / 李轩 / 李牧</li><li><span>集数: </span>10</li><li><span>开始: </span>1997</li><li><span>类型: </span>剧情</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>中国大陆</li><li><span>每集长: </span>48min</li><li><span>导演: </span>王静</li><li><span>原作: </span>李芳芳《十七岁不哭》</li>","collection":{"collect":1},"eps":[{"id":503377,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/503377","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":503378,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/503378","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":503379,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/503379","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":503380,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/503380","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":503381,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/503381","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":503382,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/503382","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":503383,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/503383","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":503384,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/503384","type":0,"sort":8,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air